## Debugging

1. git clone git://git.debian.org/git/debian-live/config-webc.git
2. cd config-webc
3. git-branch mydebug
4. git-checkout mydebug
5. sed -i 's/stable/unstable/' webconverger/config/chroot_sources/webc.bootstrap

Run in [screen](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GNU_screen) and use [CTRL]+[a]-[H] to begin recording a log file, before a build.